<p class="medlist"><span class="title"><a href="http://oreilly.com/catalog/9780596002527/index.html">XML Schema</a></span><strong><br />

The W3C's Object-Oriented Descriptions for XML<br />

By <a href="http://www.oreillynet.com/pub/au/853">Eric van der Vlist</a></strong>
</p>
<div class="secondary">
<!-- builds links to list in sidebar -->
<!--csperl>
